@startuml
participant User
box "Cluster" #LightBlue
	participant Frontend
	participant "Cluster mediator"
	participant "Subscriber 1"
	participant "Subscriber N"
	participant "Connection Store"
end box
User -> Frontend: Connect two servers
Frontend -> "Cluster mediator": Connect two servers\nTopic: "subscription"
Frontend -> User: ok
"Cluster mediator" --> "Subscriber 1": Connect
"Cluster mediator" --> "Subscriber N": Connect
note right: Connects to the specified node only if\n the message is intended for that subscriber
"Cluster mediator" --> "Connection Store": Connect
note right: Stores the connection\n in persistent storage
@enduml